OL,5, "There was water everywhere, but not a 
OL,6, single drop to drink."                 
OL,8,FThat is how Ronju Chowdhary described  
OL,9,Fthe scene outside her house on         
OL,10,FSaturday. She lives in Udiana, a remote
OL,11,Fvillage in the north-eastern Indian    
OL,12,Fstate of Assam, which has been hit by  
OL,13,Fsevere floods.                         
OL,15,FIt had been raining incessantly, she   
OL,16,Fremembers. The water rose so quickly   
OL,17,Fthat the streets were completely       
OL,18,Fsubmerged within hours. When the water 
OL,19,Fentered their home, she says the family
OL,20,Fhuddled together in darkness trying to 
OL,21,Fkeep themselves safe.                  
